{"tid":1785830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教局涉越權清算教師 至少10人未答辯就被指專業失當","createTime":"2019-12-16T16:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T07:07:48.000Z","uid":165683,"like":99,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa7f615d41e31f0734b388ab07b0c9ce6433ec6","tid":1785830,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"教育局早前稱完成調查60宗與近期社會事件有關的教師專業操守投訴個案，當中約30宗初步成立，最嚴重可能取消其教師註冊。《蘋果》獲悉，當中至少10名教師被教育局指行為失當（misconduct），但局方調查期間並無直接接觸涉事教師，而是只按學校調查所得作為證據。直至教局發信告知其行為失當的指控初步成立時，始要求涉事老師提交書面回應，過程中未有安排會面或聆訊。有律師批評，教育局此舉「好離譜」，有違公正，可被司法覆核挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191217/60384356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F60384356&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=425e5573\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F60384356&h=4d1f8182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191217/60384356</a>"},{"pid":"52ae5cee54570308df9daf8c60f7067ee5762956","tid":1785830,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:34:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0a898d1166ecb29618315aa025fb08a4aa168b98","tid":1785830,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:36:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b302604517321ae168d1feedde7bac1f77ef8aa4","tid":1785830,"uid":208722,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄"},{"pid":"d2610caa93ca7f6064c41709ee0b71d1dde39963","tid":1785830,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\